<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَعَذَابٍ}</span> ... أَلَمٍ فِي جَسَدِيِ، وَمَالِي، وَأَهْلِي.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ارْكُضْ بِرِجْلِكَ}</span> ... اضْرِبْ بِرِجْلِكَ الأَرْضَ لِيَنْبُعَ لَكَ المَاءُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُغْتَسَلٌ بَارِدٌ}</span> ... مَاءٌ تَغْتَسِلُ بِهِ، فِيهِ شِفَاؤُكَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمِثْلَهُم مَّعَهُمْ}</span> ... زِدْنَاهُ مِثْلَهُمْ مَعَهُمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِأُوْلِي الْأَلْبَابِ}</span> ... لِأَصْحَابِ العُقُولِ السَّلِيمَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضِغْثًا}</span> ... حُزْمَةَ شَمَارِيخَ أَوْ قَبْضَةَ حَشِيشٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا تَحْنَثْ}</span> ... لَا تَنْقُضْ يَمِينَكَ الَّتِي حَلَفْتَهَا بِضَرْبِ زَوْجَتِكَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَوَّابٌ}</span> ... رَجَّاعٌ إِلَى طَاعَةِ اللهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُوْلِي الْأَيْدِي}</span> ... أَصْحَابَ القُوَّةِ فيِ الطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْأَبْصَارِ}</span> ... البَصِيرَةِ فيِ الدِّينِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَخْلَصْنَاهُم بِخَالِصَةٍ}</span> ... خَصَصْنَاهُمْ بِخَصْلَةٍ عَظِيمَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِكْرَى الدَّارِ}</span> ... تَذَكُّرُ الآخِرَةِ فيِ قُلُوبِهِمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
